### Constraints (in code)

- `courtW` / `courtH` update via court `onLayout`
- `handleLayout` skips ball reposition when `isPlaying` (active rally)
- `updateCourtBounds` only sets state when bounds actually change (avoids layout loops)
- Gesture clamp uses `courtW` (portrait) or `courtH` (landscape) on movable axis

