**Goal:** Centered scoreboard in both orientations.

### Current layout (`GameScreen`)

```tsx
<>
  <SafeAreaView edges={['top', 'left', 'right', 'bottom']}>
    {isPortrait && <ScoreBoard variant="portrait" />}

    <View style={playArea}>
      <GestureDetector>
        <View style={playAreaInner}>
          <View court key={isPortrait ? 'portrait' : 'landscape'} onLayout={handleLayout}>
