## Phase4 — Portrait Play Board ✅

**Goal:** Smaller court below HUD with top/bottom paddle gameplay.

### Done

- [x] Fixed portrait court in `portraitPlayArea`, centered
- [x] `COURT_ASPECT_RATIO_PORTRAIT = 9/16`
- [x] Top/bottom paddle physics + `Paddle horizontal={isPortrait}`
- [x] Playability on small/large phones *(scaling via `courtMetrics`)*

### Sizing formula

```
maxW = screenW * 0.90
maxH = (screenH - safeInsets - HUD_BAR_HEIGHT) * 0.85
courtW = maxW; courtH = courtW / (9/16)
if courtH > maxH → courtH = maxH; courtW = courtH * (9/16)
```

